Susan Traylor https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Susan_Traylor 0 Susan Traylor is an American actress and filmmaker. She was nominated for the Independent Spirit Award for Best Female Lead for her performance in Valerie Flake (1999). Traylor's starring role in Valerie Flake also won the inaugural best feature award at The Women's Image Network Awards. Susan_Traylor is an_American_actress_and_filmmaker .
